    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "1 week ago I have ordered a pair of leather shoes from your online store. I am writing this letter to express my dissatisfaction with the product I received.",
        "The shoes I have ordered are from a luxury brand in size 9 . However, I am astonished that I received the product from some other brand which is a first copy of the luxury brand. In fact, even the logo is slightly different from the original one. Moreover, I received a size 6 pair instead of a size 9. Contrary to what  was mentioned on the site, it is not a cruelty-free product. Although, the quality is good there is no warranty card in the box.  I am disappointed with this as I wanted to wear them for a crucial event.",
        "I would like you to arrange a pick-up for these shoes and replace them with the genuine brand with shoe size in 9.  Please refund my money, unless you cannot replace it.",
        "Looking forward to hearing from you immediately.",
        "Kind Regards,",
        "Priya"
